WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:04.880
This is our secret formula to working&nbsp;
pain-free at our desk. It may sound weird,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:04.880 --> 00:00:10.560
but a good 50% of our time is spent sitting on&nbsp;
the floor on a cushion or a meditation bench,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:10.560 --> 00:00:16.080
which is more comfortable than you might imagine.&nbsp;
Like stock pictures of people meditating, on&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:20.080
the floor, we find ourselves naturally&nbsp;
sitting upright and keeping an aligned&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:25.760
posture. We also subconsciously shift between&nbsp;
different positions, and as the saying goes,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:25.760 --> 00:00:31.680
motion is lotion. But the good thing about a&nbsp;
floor-to-standing desk like the marinamantra Flow&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:31.680 --> 00:00:37.360
is we're not stuck to only sitting on the floor.&nbsp;
About 20% of the time we'll be standing, another&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:42.160
20% of the time will be sitting on a balance&nbsp;
ball, and the remainder of the time we have&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:42.160 --> 00:00:47.600
the miscellaneous stuff like one of my favorites,&nbsp;
stretching the hip flexors. But no matter how you&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:47.600 --> 00:00:52.720
choose to work at your desk, just make sure to&nbsp;
add more movement, even micro movement to your day.

